data.title: English Literature
data.meta_description: English Literature - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document is an introduction to a textbook on highlights of English literature. It provides an outline of the major periods of English literature from the Old English period to the 20th century. The Old English period from 450-1066 AD is discussed, noting the influx of Anglo-Saxon tribes and their displacement of native Britons. This period was marked by the development of Old English poetry like Beowulf and prose works under King Alfred.
